<div class="dcart-body">

  <div class="dcart-intro">
    <p>
      <strong>Disc-coveries</strong> previously included AI-generated artwork.
      To comply with Foundry’s new policy, this is no longer bundled
      with the module.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can continue without it and add your own images at any time,
      or download the original artwork from GitHub now.
    </p>
    <p class="dcart-note">
      <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
      This choice is saved per world and won’t be shown again.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="dcart-options">
    <button id="dcart-btn-decline" class="dcart-btn dcart-btn--decline">
      <i class="fas fa-image"></i>
      <span class="dcart-btn-title">Skip artwork</span>
      <span class="dcart-btn-sub">I’ll use my own images</span>
    </button>

    <button id="dcart-btn-accept" class="dcart-btn dcart-btn--accept">
      <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
      <span class="dcart-btn-title">Download artwork</span>
      <span class="dcart-btn-sub">Use the original AI-generated set</span>
    </button>
  </div>

  <div class="dcart-progress" style="display:none;">
    <div class="dcart-bar-track">
      <div class="dcart-bar-fill"></div>
    </div>
    <p class="dcart-status">Starting download…</p>
  </div>

</div>